 emission in the general context of quasar parameter space\nin order to understand quasar feedback in the form of [OIII] outflows. The\ncalibrated one-dimensional near-IR spectra are made publicly available, along\nwith a composite spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Nov 2015 20:59:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
