uss the role of the spectral flow automorphism and provide a\nconjecture for the form of the semiclassical BPS bounds in general N=2\ntwo-dimensional CFTs with extended symmetry algebras.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Nov 2015 22:31:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 May 2016 21:19:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-09"}
