esonance region and\nat low energy, consistently with experiments. For a more detailed agreement\nwith the data, the calculation suggests the inclusion of the three-phonon\nstates as well as a fine tuning of the single-particle spectrum to be obtained\nby a refinement of the nuclear potential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Dec 2015 09:42:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-09"}
